ca270474-6b94-4d04-af4a-5f94b3d9168b.name: deployment_environment
ca270474-6b94-4d04-af4a-5f94b3d9168b.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment_environment') AS deployment_environment
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'jvm_class_loaded'
GROUP BY deployment_environment

e3d0421b-5a8f-457d-a694-64108dcc057d.name: service_name
e3d0421b-5a8f-457d-a694-64108dcc057d.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') AS service_name
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'jvm_class_loaded' AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment_environment') = {{.deployment_environment}}
GROUP BY service_name
